reviewText: Oh my word, where do I begin? I love disaster films and I love most that people give bad ratings to but this one is only good for one thing...to laugh and make fun of! 90% of the acting and storyline is horrible but the worst, by far, are the tsunami warning people in Hawaii.  The Dr in the robe was pretty bad too. I would never buy this movie until you watch it. It's on YouTube. This movie is the worst movie I've ever seen. I know no other way to put it. I give it a big fat -0!
